paragraph: Nathan Bartholomew Morris (born June 18, 1971) is an American baritenor, singer, businessman, and the founding member of American band Boyz II Men. He was the host of the show Hit Properties on the DIY Network where he bought and renovated a multi-million dollar home.
Nathan Morris in-depth interview by Pete Lewis, 'Blues & Soul' March 2008
Bio of Nate on Boyz II Men official website
